data.description: Beautiful home in a fantastic location! In close proximity to Ft. Bliss and just minutes from shopping, restaurants, entertainment, schools, and Loop 375, this amazing home is waiting for you. As you walk through the home you will love the open concept living space and kitchen. Your kitchen features granite countertops, ample cabinet space, an island with bar seating, a pantry, and dining room. The living room has a large window bringing in tons of natural light to the home. Your spacious primary bedroom has a bathroom with a large soaking tub, a separate shower, double sinks, and a walk-in closet. There are three other nice sized bedrooms and a full bathroom. Out back is where you will love to relax after a long day. You have a gorgeous pergola, a low maintenance yard, covered patio, and views of the mountain. This outdoor space is the perfect spot for entertaining friends and family or enjoying a quiet spring evening. Call to schedule your viewing of this fabulous home!
